{
  "stem": "18102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my mother thought that-- and both my father and mother thought that that wasn't wise, that I would be looked on as a teacher's pet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it would not do me well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for my benefit, they were going to enroll me and, in fact, brought me to be enrolled in another school in kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, war broke out right after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I never really attended first grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was going to go to another school, also a Yiddish school, but not their [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember the school in which I eventually was enrolled in for kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the war interfered anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never got to be in that school for very long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, I spoke fluently Polish as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Polish was all around us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you couldn't very well as a child not learn both languages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Yiddish was spoken in the home and Polish outside the home with non-Jews, which I could speak.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, very much so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the community life was all mostly Jewish oriented.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Except that in their case, they were also Bundisten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Bund was the socialist organization of-- for-- for Jews, and a very active, very successful socialist Bundist organization in Bialystok and throughout Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're talking many hundreds of thousands of numbers, perhaps millions of members throughout Poland of Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was a leader in that movement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if she was a leader, but certainly an avid member, an enthusiastic member.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that was a primary cultural activity of my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But beyond that, they had school activities and the kind of things that cultural oriented people would have, whether it's theater or reading circles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was certainly part of their life.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
